Package: simplr
Version: 0.1-0
Title: Basic Symbolic Expression Simplification
Description: Basic tools for symbolic expression simplification, e.g. simplify(x*1) => x, or simplify(sin(x)^2+cos(x)^2) => 1. SimplR is based on the "Expression v3" (Ev3) 1.0 system by Leo Liberti.
